Usage: ./scripts/af {COMMAND} [OPTIONS]

Core Commands:
  env                     - Manage environment selection for af + Claude MCP
    set {local|dev|stg|prod} - Persist AF_ENV, update active .claude/mcp.json, append .goalie audit
    show                  - Show current AF_ENV selection
    list                  - List supported environments
  aqe                     - AQE CLI helpers (secondary path; MCP server remains primary)
    init [--best-effort]  - Ensure .agentic-qe/memory.db exists and run 'npx aqe init'
    status                - Best-effort AQE fleet/learning status
  prod                    - Adaptive orchestrator (rotates cycle→swarm with needs assessment)
    --rotations N         - Maximum rotations (default: 3)
    --mode MODE           - Cycle mode: advisory, mutate, enforcement (default: advisory)
    --assess-only         - Only run needs assessment, don't execute
    --multipass           - Run preflight cycle+swarm with small iters to catch regressions early
    --preflight-iters N   - Preflight iters when --multipass is set (default: 5)
    --ledger-run          - Collect optional revenue attribution (ledger) metrics for this run
    --ledger-hours N      - Hours of data to include for ledger metrics (default: 6)
    --swarm-auto-compare  - When running prod-swarm from af prod, also pass --auto-compare
    --progress-tooltip MODE - Progress helper output: off|compact|rich|json|write-status-file
    --progress-status-file PATH - Status file path for write-status-file mode
    --report-md           - Write a postable Markdown report under .goalie/
    --report-md-path PATH - Output path for --report-md
    --with-monitoring     - Run full monitoring workflow after production cycles
    --with-dev-workflow [PHASE] - Run development workflow after prod (phases: swarm|integration|rust|tests|all)
    --json                - Output JSON format

  prod-cycle              - Run production cycle with WSJF prioritization
    --with-health-check   - Run pre-cycle health check (quick-health)
    --with-evidence-assess - Run post-cycle graduation assessment
    --with-full-workflow  - Enable both pre-check and post-assess

  prod-swarm              - Run production swarm comparison and analysis
    --default-emitters    - Use curated emitter set (revenue-safe + tier-depth + gaps + intent-coverage)
    --auto-compare        - Auto-run swarm-compare after saving table
    --ab-test             - Run A/B test comparing two configurations
    --winner-grade        - Print winner-grade assessment at end
    --with-health-check   - Run pre-swarm health check
    --with-evidence-assess - Run post-swarm graduation assessment
    --with-full-workflow  - Enable both pre-check and post-assess

Analysis & Insights:
  pattern-stats           - View pattern metrics and statistics
  swarm-compare           - Compare three prod-swarm TSV tables (prior/current/auto-ref)
  goalie-gaps             - Detect observability gaps (goalie readiness)
  pattern-coverage        - Report pattern instrumentation coverage
  actionable-context      - Generate actionable context insights
  allocation-efficiency   - Analyze allocation efficiency metrics
  execution-velocity      - Analyze execution velocity metrics
  flow-efficiency        - Analyze flow efficiency metrics
  revenue-impact          - Analyze revenue impact metrics
  intent-coverage         - Calculate prompt intent coverage (pattern hit%)

Goalie Artifacts:
  goalie-metrics          - View .goalie/metrics artifact
  goalie-insights         - View .goalie/insights artifact
  goalie-cycle-log       - View .goalie/cycle-log artifact
  goalie-actions          - View .goalie/actions artifact
  goalie-board            - View .goalie/board artifact

WSJF & Prioritization:
  wsjf                    - View WSJF scores for all items
  wsjf-top                - Show top WSJF items
  wsjf-by-circle          - Show WSJF scores by circle
  wsjf-replenish          - Replenish with WSJF calculation

Evidence & Graduation:
  evidence collect        - Collect evidence from emitters
  evidence assess         - Assess autocommit graduation readiness
  evidence list           - List available emitters and thresholds
  evidence enable         - Enable an emitter
  evidence disable        - Disable an emitter
  evidence view           - View evidence for a run

Global Options:
  --json                  - Output JSON format
  --help                  - Show this help message
  --version               - Show version information

Examples:
  # Adaptive rotation (recommended)
  ./scripts/af prod --rotations 3 --mode advisory

  # Basic prod-cycle
  ./scripts/af prod-cycle --mode advisory --iterations 25

  # Full workflow with health checks and graduation assessment
  ./scripts/af prod-cycle --mode advisory --iterations 25 --with-full-workflow --json

  # Production swarm with full workflow
  ./scripts/af prod-swarm --golden-iters 25 --with-full-workflow --default-emitters

  # A/B testing
  ./scripts/af prod-swarm --ab-test --variant-a-iters 25 --variant-b-iters 100 --ab-reps 3

  # Other commands
  ./scripts/af swarm-compare --prior prior.tsv --current current.tsv --auto-ref autoref.tsv --json
  ./scripts/af actionable-context --json
  ./scripts/af wsjf-top 10 --json
